# HOSTINPL 5.6

Custom PHP MVC hosting panel — **not** Laravel/Symfony.

**Maintainer:** FLOWAXY DIGITAL STUDIO (flowaxy.com) — free product  
**Original:** HOSTINPL / Samir Shelenko, Alexander Zemlyanoy (2020)

## Structure

- `index.php` → `Action` → `application/controllers/`
- Models: `application/models/{name}.php` → `{name}Model`
- Config template: `application/config.example.php` (commit this)
- Config runtime: `application/config.php` (gitignored)
- DB prod name: `hostin`
- Server logic: `application/models/servers.php`

## Deploy

- Installer: `install/install56_deb.sh`
- CDN: `https://code.flowaxy.com/hostpanel`
- Panel: `https://github.com/iteffa-works/hostinpl.pl`

## Docs & community

- `.docs/` · `AGENTS.md` · `CONTRIBUTING.md` · `CHANGELOG.md` · `ROADMAP.md`

## Rules

- Minimal diffs; legacy PHP style
- **New or modified PHP files:** use FLOWAXY file header (not legacy 2020 HOSTINPL block) — see below
- No Composer for core; Registry pattern
- Never commit `config.php` or payment secrets
- Branding: flowaxy.com / GitHub — not hostinpl.ru

